            customizationGR.addEncodedQuery(encodedQuery);

            customizationGR.addQuery('name', customizedRVANames);
            customizationGR.query();
            var rowsMatched = customizationGR.getRowCount();
            results.details[batch + 'RepOnUpgradeFalseMatched'] = rowsMatched;
            if (noUpdateTestScript == true) {
                gs.print("Customized ReplaceOnUpgrade=false RVA on this instance: " + rowsMatched);
                return;
            }
            if (rowsMatched <= 0) {
                results.details[batch + 'RepOnUpgrade'] = 0;
                return;
            }


            var records_processed_counter = 0;
            var customization_update_batcher = new Packages.com.glide.db.StatementBatcher();
            var listOfSysids = [];

            var db_update = new Packages.com.glide.db.DBUpdate(customization_update_batcher.getDBI(), 'sys_update_xml');
            while (customizationGR.next()) {
                //gs.print("rva ACL: " +  customizationGR.name + " replace_on_upgrade:" + customizationGR.replace_on_upgrade);
                db_update.clear();
                db_update.setPrimaryKeyValue(customizationGR.getUniqueValue());
                db_update.setValue('replace_on_upgrade', true);
                customization_update_batcher.addAll(db_update.toAtomic());
                records_processed_counter++;
                listOfSysids.push(customizationGR.sys_id + '');
            }
        } catch (e) {
            results.details[batch + "Error"] = 'At least one bulk update failed: ' + e;
            results.hasError = true;
        } finally {
            if (customization_update_batcher != null) {
                customization_update_batcher.close(); // commits & clears any uncommitted updates
            }

        }

        // Capture number of customized RVA records marked as "Replace On Upgrade"
        results.details[batch + 'RepOnUpgrade'] = records_processed_counter;
        if (records_processed_counter > 0) {
            results.changed = true;
        }
    },

    _execute: function(reasonForExecution, encodedQuery, runWithNoUpdates) {
        var results = {
            'changed': false,
            'hasError': false,
            'details': {},
            'reason': reasonForExecution
        };
        var customizedRVANamesBatches = this._getcustomizedRVANamesBatches();

        var noUpdateTestScript = gs.nil(runWithNoUpdates) ? false : runWithNoUpdates; // This is here just for testing/evaluation of customized record counts. Please remove all refs to this when productized into the distribution

        // Goal: De-Customize the approx. 2300 ACLs from CHG19000754 in customizedRVANamesBatches


        // The ACL list is divided into three parts to avoid query filter from having over 999 parameters which is the limit.
        for (var i = 0; i < (customizedRVANamesBatches.length); i++) {
            var customizedRVANames = customizedRVANamesBatches[i];

            // keep track of which part is being updated
            var batch = 'RVABatch' + i;


            // Update list of report view ACLs
            this._deCustomizeRVAs(customizedRVANames, batch, results, encodedQuery, noUpdateTestScript);
        }
        results.details["totalSumOfRVAsRepOnUpgradeFalseMatched"] = results.details["RVABatch0RepOnUpgradeFalseMatched"] + results.details["RVABatch1RepOnUpgradeFalseMatched"] + results.details["RVABatch2RepOnUpgradeFalseMatched"];
        results.details["totalSumOfRVAsRepOnUpgrade"] = results.details["RVABatch0RepOnUpgrade"] + results.details["RVABatch1RepOnUpgrade"] + results.details["RVABatch2RepOnUpgrade"];
        gs.print(JSON.stringify(results));

    },

    // DEF0362115: Mark Customised RVA via RVA store app as "Replace On Upgrade"=true on their sys_update_xml records so that we:
    //      a. Avoid producing too many skipped records
    //      b. Will allow future updates to RVA records
    deCustomizeRVAsUpdatedByRVAStoreApp: function(runWithNoUpdates) {
        gs.info('Uncustomise enabled/disabled RVAs - Start');

        //Capture the reason behind running this script
        var reason = "DEF0362115_SkippedRecords";
        var encodedQuery = this._getEncodedQueryForRVAsUpdatedViaStore();

        this._execute(reason, encodedQuery, runWithNoUpdates);

        gs.info('Uncustomise enabled/disabled RVAs - End');
    },

    _getEncodedQueryForRVAsUpdatedViaStore: function() {

        var gr = new GlideRecord("report_view_acl_activation_log");
        gr.addEncodedQuery("activityINenable_acls,disable_acls");
        gr.query();

        var encodedQueryList = [];
        while (gr.next()) {
            var aclsList = [];
            var acls = gr.getValue("updated_acls").split(',');
            var createdOn = gr.getValue('sys_created_on');
            for (var i = 0; i < acls.length; i++) {
                var aclName = "sys_security_acl_" + acls[i];
                aclsList.push(aclName);
            }
            if (!gs.nil(aclsList) && aclsList.length > 0)
                encodedQueryList.push('nameIN' + aclsList.join() + '^sys_updated_on=' + createdOn);
        }

        var encodedQueryFinal = encodedQueryList.join('^NQ'); //will add OR condition between each filter
        gs.info('Following encoded ACLs will be marked as not customised: ' + encodedQueryFinal);

        return encodedQueryFinal;
    },

    type: 'DeCustomizeRVAUtil'
